{"article_id":"A3a6KQd4PS44o3Jx","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The FBI has renewed its investigation into Hillary Clinton ' s secret emails ,","depth":10},{"id":1,"text":"Director James Comey told Congress in a new letter Friday ,","depth":10},{"id":2,"text":"heightening the stakes for the Democratic presidential nominee with less than two weeks before Election Day .","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"Mr. Comey said","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"his agents learned of new emails \" pertinent \" to their probe","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"while working on an unrelated case .","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"his agents need to review those messages","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"to see","depth":12},{"id":9,"text":"whether they contain classified information","depth":13},{"id":10,"text":"and whether they affect his previous decision .","depth":13},{"id":11,"text":"In July , Mr. Comey announced","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"while he determined","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"Mrs. Clinton did mishandle classified information ,","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"she was too inept","depth":13},{"id":16,"text":"to know the risks","depth":14},{"id":17,"text":"she was running ,","depth":14},{"id":18,"text":"so he couldn ' t prove","depth":14},{"id":19,"text":"she did it intentionally","depth":14},{"id":20,"text":"- undercutting a criminal case .","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"His new announcement Friday threatened to upend the presidential campaign .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"John Podesta , Mrs. Clinton ' s campaign chairman , demanded","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Mr. Comey explain what new information","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"he ' s found ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"and blamed Republicans for \" browbeating \" the FBI into Friday ' s decision .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"\" Director Comey ' s letter refers to emails","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"that have come to light in an unrelated case ,","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"but we have no idea","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"what those emails are","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"and the Director himself notes","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"they may not even be significant , \"","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"\" It is extraordinary that we would see something like this just 11 days out from a presidential election . \"","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"Mrs. Clinton ' s running mate , Sen. Tim Kaine of Virginia , said","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Mr. Comey owes the campaign and the public a \" clearer accounting \" of the new information .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"\" When you do this 11 days before a presidential election ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"and you don ' t provide many details","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"- but details apparently are being given by the FBI to the press -","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"this is very , very troubling , \"","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Mr. Kaine told VICE News .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"\" We hope","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"that the director ,","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"and we really think","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"that he should ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"give a clearer accounting of exactly what ' s going on right now . \"","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Mr. Podesta predicted","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"the FBI would come to the same conclusion this time","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"as it did in July ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"and he pointedly noted","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"that the letter was sent to eight Republican committee chairman in Congress .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"But it was also carbon-copied to the ranking Democrats .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Mr. Comey did not explain in his letter to what information the new emails contain , how long it will take","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"to evaluate them ,","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"nor how they were obtained .","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"The New York Times reported Friday","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"that the emails were snagged as part of an investigation into former Rep. Anthony Weiner , and allegations","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"he sent illicit messages through text and social media applications to a 15-year-old North Carolina girl .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"The paper reported","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"that law enforcement officials seized at least one device","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"shared by Mr. Weiner and his now estranged wife , Huma Abedin","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"- a top personal aide to Mrs. Clinton .","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"The couple announced","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"they were separating in August amid Mr. Weiner ' s involvement in another sexting scandal ,","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"but before the 15-year-old girl ' s allegations surfaced .","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"As Mrs. Clinton ' s top personal aide , Ms. Abedin also had an account on the secret Clinton email server","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"and exchanged classified information with her boss .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"Mr. Comey said","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"he was briefed on the new emails on Thursday","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"and felt","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"it was important to promptly alert Congress of investigators ' latest efforts .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"Republican leaders","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"who were among the eight recipients of the letter","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"called for further disclosures by the FBI director ,","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"with Sen. Richard C. Shelby urging him to provide additional information","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"before voters go to the polls Nov. 8 .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"\" While I am pleased","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"that the FBI is re-opening this case in light of new information ,","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"it is imperative that the Bureau immediately evaluate the material","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"to complete this investigation , \"","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"said Mr. Shelby , chairman of the Appropriations Subcommittee on Commerce , Justice , Science , and Related Agencies .","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"\" The American people are electing their next Commander-in-Chief only days from now ,","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"and they deserve to know the conclusion of your review prior to Election Day . \"","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"Sen. Charles E. Grassley ,","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"who as chairman of the Senate Judiciary Committee was one of the letter ' s recipients ,","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"Mr. Comey owes the country more of an explanation","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"about what he ' s found .","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"\" The letter from Director Comey was unsolicited and , quite honestly , surprising .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"But it ' s left a lot more questions than answers for both the FBI and Secretary Clinton , \"","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"the Iowa Republican said .","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"GOP presidential nominee Donald Trump ,","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"campaigning in Manchester , New Hampshire ,","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"he respected the FBI","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"for reversing itself .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"For her part Mrs. Clinton ,","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"campaigning in Cedar Rapids , Iowa ,","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"did not address the issue ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"instead sticking doggedly to her stump speech of attacks on Mr. Trump","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"mixed with a plea to voters","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"to focus on issues .","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"President Obama ,","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"who has been saddled by association with Mrs. Clinton ,","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"who was serving him during the time","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"she maintained her secret email server ,","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"did not respond to questions","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"shouted by reporters Friday afternoon","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"as he left the White House on a campaign trip to Florida","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"to stump for Mrs. Clinton and Democratic Senate candidate Patrick Murphy .","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"Briefing reporters on Air Force One ,","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"deputy press secretary Eric Schultz said","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"Mr. Obama President Obama expects the FBI to \" follow the facts","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"wherever they lead \"","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"and to act \" irrespective of politics . \"","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"Mr. Schultz said","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"the new email development does not affect Mr. Obama ' s support of Mrs. Clinton .","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"Libertarian candidate Gary Johnson said on CNN ,","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"\" Obviously the FBI didn ' t do this lightly .","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"There has to be something there . \"","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"He lamented the prospect of \" a president-elect under criminal investigation .","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"\" \" That ' s what ' s going to now be the case ,","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"if she is elected , \"","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"\" She will control those jobs","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"[ in the Justice Department ]","depth":14},{"id":126,"text":"that controls how this issue moves forward ,","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"which points to a special prosecutor .","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"This is a mess .","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"It ' s a mess .","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"I think","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"Trump is toast ,","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"so Hillary moving forward as president-elect ?","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"Four years of this ?","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"Ugh . \"","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"Congressional Republicans ,","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"who have been at odds with Mr. Trump on many issues ,","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"found common ground with their nominee","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"in attacking Mrs. Clinton .","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"\" This decision , long overdue , is the result of her reckless use of a private email server , and her refusal","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"to be forthcoming with federal investigators , \"","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"said House Speaker Paul D. Ryan .","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"He again called for the Obama administration to suspend the classified intelligence briefings","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"Mrs. Clinton is getting as the Democratic nominee .","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"And Sen. John Cornyn , Texas Republican , wondered","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"whether the Justice Department will now convene a grand jury","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"to pursue the case .","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"He said","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"the FBI had already cleared Mrs. Clinton of mishandling classified information ,","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"so to reopen the case suggests either potential new evidence of intent","depth":15},{"id":150,"text":"to mishandle secrets ,","depth":15},{"id":151,"text":"or other potential criminal questions .","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"\" Originally FBI focused on ' classification rules ' and not broader issues","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"related to government records/obstruction of justice .","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"Will they now ? \"","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"Mr. Cornyn tweeted .","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"An FBI spokesman declined Friday to comment on the reopening of the investigation .","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"The revelation","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"that the investigation is continuing","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"comes too late","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"to affect the 16 million voters","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"who have already cast ballots in absentee or in-person voting .","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"Republicans have said","depth":4},{"id":163,"text":"Mrs. Clinton appeared to mislead Congress in her sworn testimony to the Benghazi probe in 2015 .","depth":4},{"id":164,"text":"The staggering reversal by Mr. Comey comes","depth":5},{"id":165,"text":"as Mrs. Clinton is reeling from another electronic scandal","depth":6},{"id":166,"text":"- the revelations from emails","depth":7},{"id":167,"text":"obtained and posted by WikiLeaks from Mr. Podesta ' s personal email address .","depth":7},{"id":168,"text":"Mrs. Clinton refused to use an official state.gov email account during her four years as secretary ,","depth":7},{"id":169,"text":"instead setting up an account on a server","depth":8},{"id":170,"text":"she kept at her home in New York .","depth":8},{"id":171,"text":"That arrangement shielded her emails from public disclosure for six years ,","depth":7},{"id":172,"text":"thwarting open-records laws .","depth":7},{"id":173,"text":"She belatedly turned over some 30,000 messages","depth":7},{"id":174,"text":"she deemed government-related ,","depth":7},{"id":175,"text":"but the FBI recovered thousands of others","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"she didn ' t","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"- including some","depth":8},{"id":178,"text":"that contained classified information .","depth":8},{"id":179,"text":"- Andrea Noble and Dave Boyer contributed to this article .","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":359,"left":358,"right":179,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":358,"left":341,"right":357,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":341,"left":250,"right":340,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":250,"left":231,"right":249,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":231,"left":213,"right":230,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":213,"left":201,"right":212,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":190,"right":200,"relation":"